m zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532788\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532788\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104uow1665702572236.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uow1665702572236.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uow1665702572236.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uow1665702572236\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"uow1665702572236__lfilemove_226491\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Move a local file to a local directory, ignoring any file redirections in the assignment file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"uow1665702572236__topic_d74021e1_d74022e1_d74023e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uow1665702572236__p_d74024e1_d74025e1_d74026e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lfilemove</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FilePath</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DirPath</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">NewFilePath</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"uow1665702572236__section_w1659ab1b7b5_w1660ab1b7_w1661ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uow1665702572236__p_d74027e1_d74028e1_d74029e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">lfilemove \"./test1.txt\", \"./saved/text.txt\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uow1665702572236__topic_d48752e1_d48753e1_d48754e1_d48755e1_d48756e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d284305e85\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"uow1665702572236__d5913e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uow1665702572236__d5913e20__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uow1665702572236__d5913e20__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uow1665702572236__d5913e20__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__d5913e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FilePath</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__d5913e20__entry__2\">String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__d5913e20__entry__3\">File name, optionally preceded by the path\n\t\t\t\t to the file. Must not end with a directory separator.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__d5913e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DirPath</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__d5913e20__entry__2\">String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__d5913e20__entry__3\">Directory name, optionally preceded by the path\n                        to the directory. Must end with a directory separator. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__d5913e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NewFilePath</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__d5913e20__entry__2\">String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__d5913e20__entry__3\">New file name, optionally preceded by the\n\t\t\t\t path to the file. Must not end with a directory separator.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uow1665702572236__topic_d48757e1_d48758e1_d48759e1_d48760e1_d48761e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d284305e169\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"uow1665702572236__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uow1665702572236__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uow1665702572236__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__2\">Error constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uow1665702572236__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__3\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__3\">Successful</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-13</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UIOSERR_OS_COMMAND&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uow1665702572236__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__3\">An error occurred while trying to perform the\n                     OS command. Set <code class=\"ph codeph\">/pri=64</code> to display the exact error in the\n                     message frame.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uow1665702572236__topic_d48762e1_d48763e1_d48764e1_d48765e1_d48766e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d284305e256\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uow1665702572236__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"uow1665702572236__topic_d48767e1_d48768e1_d48769e1_d48770e1_d48771e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d284305e265\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uow1665702572236__p_d74048e1_d74049e1_d74050e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lfilemove</span> statement moves the specified file <var class=\"keyword varname\">FilePath</var> to the target location, but ignores any file redirections in the assignment file.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uow1665702572236__p_d74051e1_d74052e1_d74053e1\">If you want to move a file from or to a network location, use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">fileload</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uow1665702572236__p_d74054e1_d74055e1_d74056e1\">In other respects, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lfilemove</span> behaves like <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">filemove</span>. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fki1720023320095.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fki1720023320095.html\" title=\"Move the specified file to the target location.\">filemove</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"uow1665702572236__note_w1662ab1b7c13b9_w1663ab1b7c13_w1664ab1b7_w1665ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> To rename a file without moving it, use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lfilerename</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">filerename</span>.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bau1719406118842.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ProcScript for File System Management</a><p>Uniface provides ProcScript statements and functions for managing local files and directories.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qxw1665702569337.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Zip Files</a><p>Zip files (or archives) contain one or more files that have been compressed or stored using the zip file format. Uniface supports the use of zip files for export, import, data conversion, file handling, compilation, and assignment redirection.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oyn1665702570922.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>lfilerename</a><p>Rename a file in the same directory, ignoring any file redirections in the assignment file.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/njw1665702571289.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$TEXT_FILE_EXTENSIONS</a><p>Specify the file extensions that are treated as text files, rather than binary files.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532788\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532788\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "lfilemove Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Move a local file to a local directory, ignoring any file redirections in the assignment file. lfilemove FilePath , DirPath | NewFilePath Example: lfilemove \"./test1.txt\", \"./saved/text.txt\" Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description FilePath String File name, optionally preceded by the path to the file. Must not end with a directory separator. DirPath String Directory name, optionally preceded by the path to the directory. Must end with a directory separator. NewFilePath String New file name, optionally preceded by the path to the file. Must not end with a directory separator. Return Values Table 2. Values returned by $procerror Value Error constant Meaning 0 Successful -13 <UIOSERR_OS_COMMAND> An error occurred while trying to perform the OS command. Set /pri=64 to display the exact error in the message frame. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The lfilemove statement moves the specified file FilePath to the target location, but ignores any file redirections in the assignment file. If you want to move a file from or to a network location, use fileload . In other respects, lfilemove behaves like filemove . For more information, see filemove . Note: To rename a file without moving it, use lfilerename or filerename . Related Links ProcScript for File System Management Uniface provides ProcScript statements and functions for managing local files and directories. Zip Files Zip files (or archives) contain one or more files that have been compressed or stored using the zip file format. Uniface supports the use of zip files for export, import, data conversion, file handling, compilation, and assignment redirection. lfilerename Rename a file in the same directory, ignoring any file redirections in the assignment file. $TEXT_FILE_EXTENSIONS Specify the file extensions that are treated as text files, rather than binary files. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}